Text: Re Meeting fwdBradley Romine EESOR Stanford University Forwarded message Date Thu Jan PST From bradley romine tanfordEDU To Nick Bambos Subject Re Meeting Professor Bambos pm on Wed is fine with them So Ill see you then in your office in terman Brad On Thu Jan Nick Bambos wrote Brad Yes I would be happy to meet with them How about pm on Wed Thanks Nick bradley romine wrote Hello Professor Bambos I was talking to some friends I have at Enron about pricing options for bandwidth trading and other optimization algorithms for broadband networks Anyway they are interested in talking to you about your research They will be in town next week tuesday and wednesday and would appreciate getting a chance to talk to you Are you available Thanks Brad Bradley Romine EESOR Stanford University Bradley Romine EESOR Stanford University
